The Facebook post, while featuring an image of individuals associated with the PNL, does not constitute electoral propaganda under Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015. The content aligns more with journalistic reporting than with electoral campaigning.  The absence of explicit endorsements, candidate mentions, or calls to action related to the parliamentary elections further supports this conclusion.
